## 3. RESTRICTIONS

### 3.1 Distribution
You MAY NOT:
- Redistribute the Mod or any modified version without explicit written permission
- Upload the Mod to any website, mod platform, or file-sharing service
- Include the Mod in mod packs without explicit written permission
- Sell, rent, lease, or otherwise charge money for access to the Mod
- Claim the Mod or any of its assets as your own work

### 3.2 Modification & Derivative Works
You MAY NOT: 
- Publicly distribute modified versions of the Mod
- Extract assets from the Mod for use in other projects (unless you created them)
- Reverse-engineer compiled code beyond what is provided in source form
- Create derivative mods that modify the Mod's core files without permission

**Note:** This restriction does NOT apply to companion mods (see Section 2.3)

### 3.3 Official Distribution Channels
Official releases are ONLY available through:
- CurseForge:   https://www.curseforge.com/hytale/mods/golds-beasts-rebalance
- GitHub: https://github.com/CGGrimsley/GBR_DEV

Any distribution through other channels is unauthorized and violates this license.

