  - Project direction and design

### 5.2 Asset Rights

**Core Assets (Created by kdrgold):**
- **All Rights Reserved**
- Property of kdrgold and The Gold's Beasts Rebalance Team
- Not licensed for use outside of this Mod

**Contributor Assets (Option A - Copyright Assigned):**
- Copyright transfers to kdrgold
- Subject to the same rights as core assets
- May be used in any way by the project owner

**Contributor Assets (Option B - Retained Ownership):**
- Copyright remains with original creator
- Licensed exclusively to this Mod under the terms in Section 4.1 Option B
- Creator credited in assets documentation
- May be extracted by original creator for their own use

